{"tid":598168,"cid":10,"subCid":0,"title":"打LOL掛網常被罵，男大生截圖報案成功告20人兼拿和解金","createTime":"2018-03-19T09:42:03.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-19T10:14:27.000Z","uid":1886,"like":8,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"7117136c00cff7db36e44c43d88c8e5605fbc1f7","tid":598168,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-19T09:42:03.000Z","msg":"桃園一名私立大學何姓男學生（24歲），常上網玩「英雄聯盟」線上遊戲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，並與其他隊友一起競賽，疑似常故意掛網<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 、放慢速度玩遊戲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，遭隊友辱罵「豬隊友<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 」、「智障<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 」，男大生截圖<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 後，提告隊友妨害名譽<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，部分被控網友不想走司法途徑，與男大生和解，警方受理超過20件，直呼男大生根本拿檢警當提款機。<br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://img.appledaily.com.tw/images/ReNews/20180318/640_ccd768cf4aed3875cec4c720a23bbcef.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.appledaily.com.tw%2Fimages%2FReNews%2F20180318%2F640_ccd768cf4aed3875cec4c720a23bbcef.jpg&h=d7290028&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n全文：<br />\n<a href=\"https://tw.appledaily.com/new/realtime/20180318/1315305/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Fnew%2Frealtime%2F20180318%2F1315305%2F&d=dYNBpw77B42fMm44Tyl9p1eK4D04he4k8uKHxpzC8zE%3D&h=e91f92e1\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Fnew%2Frealtime%2F20180318%2F1315305%2F&h=1f4ccf56\" target=\"_blank\">https://tw.appledaily.com/new/realtime/20180318/1315305/</a></div>"},{"pid":"56a3b67210cdfd865552fa90ad6162047f99654e","tid":598168,"uid":1886,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-19T09:43:40.000Z","msg":"何姓大學生今年就讀某大學4年級，喜歡玩線上遊戲，報名組隊參與英雄聯盟遊戲對打。他疑似刻意掛網不打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，導致隊友生氣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 、辱罵<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 。他多次截圖，將隊友罵他的字眼到派出所報案<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，提告對方妨害名譽，有時一次提告4、5位。這名大學生，多次截隊友辱罵他「白痴」、「笨蛋」、「低能」、「智障」、「豬隊友」等字眼，到派出所提告隊友妨害名譽。<br />\n<br />\n網路電競對打，一般人都使用網路暱稱、代號，派出所受理報案後交給偵查隊，再由偵查隊行文給線上遊戲公司，查閱辱罵男大生的隊友的資料，部分隊友家住南部，接獲警方傳喚通知後，因不想走冗長的司法途徑，決定與男大生和解，男大生因而獲得賠償兩萬元（約港幣$5382）。"},{"pid":"983f62ba0b702e222f25ea975e5ae7050af3ad15","tid":598168,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-19T09:43:52.000Z","msg":"因為反覆實施，檢警認為，這名男大生利用這種方式，狀告隊友，彷彿把檢警當提款機。警方曾試圖詢問男大生，為何提告隊友，男大生表達，之前玩線上遊戲時辱罵對方，對方不放過，他因而上法院。警方告訴男大生，提告妨害名譽是他的權益，但也委婉提醒男大生，大學生應該專心課業，不要太過沈迷電玩，不過男大生似乎沒有聽進去。<br />\n<br />\n律師湯偉指出，意圖散布於眾，而指摘或傳述足以毀損他人名譽之事者，為誹謗罪，處一年以下有期徒刑、拘役或五百元以下罰金。妨害名譽屬告訴乃論，需由當事人提告。"},{"pid":"8e971dda456eedb147098a0a25931f2c80a5fee9","tid":598168,"uid":18366,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-19T09:45:32.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"c00b2faf03062b3d8b99e44b7e21e7029b5e80be","tid":598168,"uid":87971,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-19T09:47:04.000Z","msg":"係台灣窮人都可以玩法律"},{"pid":"d54defd79580c4e1f18d4a8aa32e9ff8e13c6493","tid":598168,"uid":106614,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-19T09:47:47.000Z","msg":"返工掛下機又賺一筆<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"84f23cdb1550c1350cda607a02c38fae2409161c","tid":598168,"uid":83340,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-19T09:53:13.000Z","msg":"上網罵鳩d台仔最開心，一話佢就話要提告我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6f47ec6a4b681b72629b145473b45cb639e7fc26","tid":598168,"uid":30510,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-19T09:55:18.000Z","msg":"最鍾意屈地區<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\